    npcPos: 76
    npcSprite: {fileID: -1018686373385036869, guid: 0060de204d35a494da2ce31a2aed8053, type: 3}
    lines:
    - 'So if I want to create a varaible called myNum that stores the number 10,
      I type:

      int myNum = 10;

      Is that it?'
  - npcName: Morgan
    showNpc: 1
    npcPos: 82
    npcSprite: {fileID: 5927882187559961596, guid: 5b6284e1a3b3206428453b030857c481, type: 3}
    lines:
    - 'Right. Also note that there''s rules to naming variables: it cannot start
